name: J&V LOGISTICS & TRANSPORT
tag_list: logistics, manpower, transport, shipping, labour-supply, forwarding
overview: J&V Logistics & Transport (MALAYSIA), incorporated in 2010 being a fully owned Malaysian base organization headquartered at JOHOR BAHRU and is Leading International Freight Forwarder by providing Quality Logistics services worldwide. As a member of T Swift Group of Companies which was formed under the direction of Joseph Cheng & Viveka Lim, our ambitious is to enhance the betterment of living at all levels. In association with the joint force from our Global Logistics Partners, we are able to perform business internationally with local expertise, a formula that has proved highly successful and which offers a platform for future development.We believe that, with wider international coverage and our expertise in total logistics freight Forwarding for both Ocean and Air as well as Local Distribution, J&V Logistics & Transport (MALAYSIA) will certainly reach greater height in time to come.
